description:
&lt;p&gt;A friendly GP Practice requires a full-time receptionists with some administration duties. The position is suited to someone with System One experience who has worked on a patient focused role previously, but suitable for anyone with the experience within the customer focused environment. The working hours will be Monday – Friday; 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful applicants will provide reception services to the patients and medical professionals, working alongside an excellent team who are constantly striving to provide an excellent primary care service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary is dependent on the experience. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more details please contact Dr Mohammed Islam on 01623 440018 or email mohammed.Islam16@nhs.&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;net&lt;/span&gt;  (Practice Manager).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply by completing the NHS Jobs application form and attach your CV. We do not accept CVs on it’s own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: Tuesday 10th Nov 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview: Friday 13th Nov 2020 &amp; Monday 16th Nov 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants don’t need to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that only successful candidates will be contacted for the interview. If you don’t hear us within 2 weeks after the closure of the advert then you have to assume that you are not shortlisted for the positions.&lt;/p&gt;
